data.text:
The embodiment of Renaissance humanist thinking, Leonardo da Vinci died May 2, 1519.

Born in Vinci, Republic of Florence and died in Clos Lucé, Amboise, Kingdom of France.

500th Anniversary of Death of Leonardo da Vinci

Issued by Italy February 5, 2019

Designer: Istituto Poligrafico e Zecca dello Stato

500th Anniversary of Death of Leonardo da Vinci

Issued by France, October 28, 2019
